title: PASCAR set for final race
text:
PASCAR set for final race By: Uncredited Report Error 
The Prairie Association of Stock Car Racing will hold its final race day of the season on Sunday at the Souris Speedway. 
It will be the seventh race day of the season for PASCAR, which staged five days of racing last year in its inaugural season. 
Racing begins at 1 p.m., and is free, although donations are accepted.
